post.description:
This operation returns account balance
				information.
This operation retrieves account details information.
This operation returns account transactions.

This operation enables Registration and
				De-registration of a Custometer and Accounts for MT940 services

This operation provide an option to download the
				MT940 messages for the entitled accounts

This operation provide an option to download the
				MT942 messages for the entitled accounts
This operation provide an option to validate the BBAN and IBAN
This operation is used to create the IBAN
This operation is used to get the PromoCodes
This operation is used to get the TransactionCodes

This service provides XLS information (i.e. RFM
				Visit and Amount Counters as well as
				Last Visit Date, Pool, E-Coupon
				balances and Definition Attributes) that
				are related to the
				Media/Card level or Customer Account level.

This service is used to redeem awards from an
				Account or Media
This operation retrieves CMS Accounts details
Inquiring SAMA Standing Orde
Inquiring Customer Standing Order
this service is used to cancelthe standing order
this service is used to update the standing order
The function is used to request for the status information of an account in SigCap.

To get the Payroll details(007088.xml) and To
				change customer to NON Payroll (007089.xml)
				that to be decided based
				on the operationMode(R=Retrieve, U=Update) in
				the request.

This operation is used to Inquiry account
				transactions.

This operation is used to do real time pledging
				of
				time deposit Collaterals.

This operation is used for getting the CMS
				account transaction using pagination

This Operation will fetch Cumulative Balance of
				all the active Omni Accounts and Current Accounts linked to a CIF

This Operation will fetch Corporate
				MT940Statement from other banks through SWIFT Network
